<section class="brand-story">
  <div class="story-container">
    <div class="image-column">
      <img src="/brand-story-image.jpg" alt="A sophisticated spirits setting" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="text-column">
      <h2 class="title">Born From Adventure. <br/> Built For The Journey.</h2>
      <p>
        Jerry Can Spirits wasn't conceived in a boardroom. It was born from windswept coastlines, navigated through rugged highlands, and shared around campfires. It's a tribute to the legacy of the jerry can itselfâ€”a symbol of unwavering reliability and resourcefulness.
      </p>
      <p>
        We craft spirits with that same purpose. No shortcuts, no compromises. Just functional, exceptional spirits engineered in the UK for those who value substance over style. This is your standard issue.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .brand-story {
    background-color: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .story-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .image-column img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 500px;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* --- CHANGED --- */
  .title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--cream); /* Explicitly set title to light */
  }

  /* --- CHANGED --- */
  .text-column p {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--cream); /* Changed from slate */
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9; /* Slight opacity makes body text softer than headlines */
  }

  /* Responsive styles for smaller screens */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .story-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack the columns */
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .text-column {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>